<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.20">
<l>aḻakiya paimpoṉṉiṉ kōlaṅkaik koṇṭu</l>
<l>kaḻalkaḷ cataṅkai kalanteṅku mārppa</l>
<l>maḻakaṉ ṟiṉaṅkaḷ maṟittut tirivāṉ</l>
<l>kuḻalka ḷiruntavā kāṇīrē kuvimulai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You round breasted [ladies], see the quality of the curls of him</l>
<l>who wanders herding the groups of young claves with a beautiful staff</l>
<l>of green gold in the palm of [his] hand [and] as a string of small bells</l>
<l>and anklets mingle and resound everywhere. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
